Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（本片開始）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.09,0:00:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮得不错哦   -是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚐嚐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  奈奈美應該會喜歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何   -好吃   -真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.10,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是裕也做的嗎   -嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃  羡慕你的未来的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福哦  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.05,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都没交女友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦   -未来都還没决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为這個不交嗎   -這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都不主動一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都不出門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜   -我不喜歡那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真固執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是國中時来這的   -對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當时是國小   -對  所以你把我當小孩看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會叫我姐姐   -好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是命令你嗎   -對  當时還好有她教你唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只聽你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了   -再喝點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了   -又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃   -慢吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.05,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕也是個好孩子  真的没女友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許對女生没興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧   -不知耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經驗也很多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳老公有小三哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還正值新婚期耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的路還很長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.15,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣   -對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟老師您說真是太好了   -才不是老師  是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的相遇最好   -對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪愈大想的事就不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻也是   -對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  要一起喝嗎   -不  我是口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别偷看她洗澡哦   -才不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會我去洗  你先跟她喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟你這樣喝酒好開心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.11,0:09:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對   -你常喝酒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没喝了  我老公不喜歡我喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我老公會去酒店裡喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧   -他說應酬没辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的没交過女友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧   -又来了   -哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.17,0:10:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們小時親過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟姐姐接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.13,0:11:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就親過了   -那是以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.14,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的接吻是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.13,0:15:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.13,0:15:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起吧   -不  晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.14,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.08,0:15:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你不會来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来摸我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.17,0:21:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.09,0:23:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱熱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.15,0:24:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.16,0:26:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃   -好舒服哦   -是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.05,0:27:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑滑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.06,0:27:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑滑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.06,0:27:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.13,0:27:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.10,0:28:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来舔我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.06,0:28:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.13,0:28:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.11,0:30:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.14,0:31:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.06,0:32:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.10,0:32:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.11,0:34:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.12,0:34:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.11,0:35:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以插入嗎   -可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.17,0:36:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.10,0:39:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.10,0:39:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.06,0:40:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.15,0:40:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.16,0:40:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.10,0:40:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.16,0:42:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服   -一起舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.16,0:42:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.08,0:43:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.11,0:50:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:00.12,0:51:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.16,0:51:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.10,0:51:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射好多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.08,0:52:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.04,0:53:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:07.05,0:53:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽呢   -喝太多了 還在睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:17.06,0:53:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完早餐一起去散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.13,0:53:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.13,0:53:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都變好多了  好懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:37.08,0:53:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳没變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:42.15,0:53:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還没叫我姐耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.15,0:53:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是真的姐弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.16,0:53:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻像的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.17,0:54:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們常在這兒玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.11,0:54:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像回到小時的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:22.05,0:54:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚做了不該做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.06,0:54:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像當時是我的惡作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.15,0:54:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.08,0:54:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.16,0:55:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:07.17,0:55:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多鞋子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:13.04,0:55:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:36.13,0:55:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.13,0:55:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被你媽發现的  而且我結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.07,0:55:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳老公也有小三  但並不表示我能有小王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.08,0:56:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍未條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:02.15,0:56:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:32.05,0:56:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我偷看妳洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:45.13,0:56:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:57.14,0:57:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:04.08,0:57:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.04,0:58:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:40.04,0:58:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被你媽發现的  冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:02.07,0:59:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳看著我就好   -我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.16,0:59:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年来的每一天  我還想著妳邊打手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.11,0:59:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我興奮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:58.12,1:00:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:10.13,1:00:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近一點看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.04,1:00:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.11,1:00:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别出聲一起自慰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.12,1:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐口水吧   -好害羞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:39.13,1:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:52.16,1:13:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.04,1:14:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:55.15,1:14:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.12,1:15:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射好多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:54.14,1:15:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:08.16,1:16:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:18.04,1:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕也你在房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:23.11,1:16:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:23.24,1:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
