Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:24.84,1:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:27.11,1:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:27.78,1:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:27.91,1:16:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:51.13,1:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.15,1:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小孩都很安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.15,1:17:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老了   -哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:17.16,1:17:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.10,1:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交了男朋友   -什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:29.04,1:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎  還好有她來  我可以出去約會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.05,1:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯耶  對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.12,1:17:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.13,1:17:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的人   -是學生的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:56.13,1:17:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽過世  一個人扶養孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:04.14,1:18:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀比我大啦
